        "subject": "LU-3346 obt: Completely remove the usage of obt_sb",
        "message": "LU-3346 obt: Completely remove the usage of obt_sb\n\nThe assignment of obt->obt_sb was removed in a recent project.\nThe peace of code with obt->obt_sb usage from this function has\nnever executed because of smart compiler remove it. This BUG\nwas not discovered because we have IR so that even the timeout\nis much short it can still survive.\n\nSigned-off-by: Dmitry Eremin <dmitry.eremin@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I4b87e887e4f8799814883ca0a58193446c418739\n"
      },
